{"tid":1405484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 濫權警察紅燈過馬路唔駛你教！","createTime":"2019-08-04T09:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T21:15:09.000Z","uid":266968,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fced6e097ce715356d195dd03c702af2962d0434","tid":1405484,"uid":266968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:55:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/673975979716035/posts/703097386803894?s=100000826367660&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F673975979716035%2Fposts%2F703097386803894%3Fs%3D100000826367660%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB9HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=da979139\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/673975979716035/posts/703097386803894?s=100000826367660&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨晚（4日）黃大仙爆發警民衝突，警方出動催淚彈驅散向其喝罵的街坊，更有警員在橫過馬路時，疑未有留意交通燈號，在紅燈時走出斑馬線，險被一輛遵守交通規則的汽車撞倒。惟該警員似未察覺有關情況，反而揮棍指嚇司機，整個過程被涉事車輛的行車記錄儀拍下，並被上載至「前線警員支持大聯盟」fb專頁。"},{"pid":"fc9307bdc66d15005249a4964b541283442e9194","tid":1405484,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:57:27.000Z","msg":"dum唔切會點<br />\n同埋舉棍做咩認真<br />\n係咪以為自己可以剎停部車"},{"pid":"2aea0cf581747bb20313a45e1f82f06d5889cef1","tid":1405484,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:57:57.000Z","msg":"成撚日講破壞法治 根本係班狗係度破壞緊"},{"pid":"6174eff553803165d2751a76a63ed277fc233aa3","tid":1405484,"uid":135867,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XTxY5A7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXTxY5A7.gif&h=0883ad2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c2583014d2ddda9326328a0d25b80d42d23d049","tid":1405484,"uid":272119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:01:21.000Z","msg":"教壞小朋友"},{"pid":"54ebe48f3754fdba4e334f83f8e92a6c1f37c42d","tid":1405484,"uid":266968,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":